---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  lang="en"
  title="Privacy Policy | Sahloo سهلو"
  description="Sahloo Privacy Policy — we collect no personal data. All calculations happen in your browser."
  canonical="https://sahloo.com/en/privacy/"
>
<main id="main">
  <div class="page-hero"><div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="breadcrumb"><a href="#" class="lang-switch">Home</a><span class="bc-sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span aria-current="page">Privacy Policy</span></nav>
<script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://sahloo.com/en/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Privacy Policy"}]}</script>
    <h1 style="margin-top:14px;">🔒 Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>We respect your privacy.</p>
  </div></div>
  <div class="container" style="padding-bottom:64px;">
    <div class="prose">
    <h2>Our Commitment to Your Privacy</h2>
    <p>Sahloo is built with privacy in mind. We do not collect, store, or share any personal information about you.</p>
    <h2>What We Collect</h2>
    <p><strong>Nothing.</strong> All calculations on Sahloo happen entirely in your browser (client-side JavaScript). No data is ever sent to our servers.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>We do not require registration or login</li>
      <li>We do not use cookies for tracking</li>
      <li>We do not use advertising networks</li>
      <li>We do not sell or share any data</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>We may use privacy-respecting, anonymized analytics (e.g. page view counts only) to understand which tools are most useful. No personally identifiable information is ever collected.</p>
    <h2>External Services</h2>
    <p>The Currency Converter tool fetches live exchange rates from <a href="https://www.exchangerate-api.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ExchangeRate-API.com</a>. When you use this tool, your browser makes a request to their API. Please refer to their privacy policy for details.</p>
    <p>Fonts are loaded from Google Fonts. Google may log font requests per their privacy policy.</p>
    <h2>Children</h2>
    <p>Sahloo does not knowingly collect any information from children under 13.</p>
    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy occasionally. The date of the last update will be noted here.</p>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2026</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? <a href="/en/contact/">Contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
</Layout>
